1
00:01:36,570 --> 00:01:39,870
[NORTHWARD]

2
00:01:40,060 --> 00:01:42,030
[Episode 12]

3
00:01:42,190 --> 00:01:42,420
No.

4
00:01:42,420 --> 00:01:43,990
I want to play with the dog.

5
00:01:44,270 --> 00:01:45,280
Fenghua!

6
00:01:46,590 --> 00:01:47,330
Look.

7
00:01:47,509 --> 00:01:48,180
Here.

8
00:01:48,270 --> 00:01:49,570
This is your little brother.

9
00:01:49,670 --> 00:01:50,340
When you have time,

10
00:01:50,340 --> 00:01:51,950
take him for a walk around the street.

11
00:01:51,950 --> 00:01:52,950
It's his first time here.

12
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:53,750
Fenghua is busy.

13
00:01:53,750 --> 00:01:54,810
She needs to do her homework.

14
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,690
The college entrance exam is next year.

15
00:01:56,950 --> 00:01:58,550
She doesn't have time.

16
00:01:58,580 --> 00:01:59,610
I have time. I have time.

17
00:01:59,870 --> 00:02:01,320
Homework can be done anytime.

18
00:02:01,340 --> 00:02:02,030
Let's go, little brother.

19
00:02:02,230 --> 00:02:03,110
I'll take you out to play.

20
00:02:03,110 --> 00:02:04,070
There's no need to be polite with your sister.

21
00:02:04,070 --> 00:02:04,950
I want to go play by the river.

22
00:02:04,950 --> 00:02:05,750
Fenghua.

23
00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:08,710
You don't have to buy too many of those osmanthus cakes that I like!

24
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,570
Two catties would be enough!

25
00:02:10,990 --> 00:02:13,470
I haven't heard her call me Grandma since I got here!

26
00:02:13,550 --> 00:02:14,990
Who taught her such manners?

27
00:02:14,990 --> 00:02:15,830
What do you mean she didn't?

28
00:02:15,870 --> 00:02:16,710
She called you as soon as she came in.

29
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:17,740
You didn't hear it?

30
00:02:17,870 --> 00:02:19,720
My ears are deaf. I didn't hear it!

31
00:02:20,970 --> 00:02:22,180
Sister-in-law,

32
00:02:22,270 --> 00:02:23,430
I didn't hear it either.

33
00:02:23,450 --> 00:02:24,890
Then your hearing must be pretty bad.

34
00:02:25,310 --> 00:02:26,150
Alright, Mom,

35
00:02:26,190 --> 00:02:26,710
don't be angry.

36
00:02:26,710 --> 00:02:27,510
What kind of mother is she?

37
00:02:27,510 --> 00:02:28,270
She's just a bad person.

38
00:02:28,270 --> 00:02:29,980
Can't even raise a child properly.

39
00:02:30,230 --> 00:02:32,329
Like mother, like daughter.

40
00:02:32,790 --> 00:02:34,020
She's always been like this.

41
00:02:40,370 --> 00:02:41,720
What's your name?

42
00:02:41,990 --> 00:02:44,170
You mean my original name or my current one?

43
00:02:44,510 --> 00:02:46,000
How many names do you have?

44
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,770
I used to be called Xiaojun,

45
00:02:47,950 --> 00:02:50,070
but now Grandma calls me Xiaobao.

46
00:02:50,070 --> 00:02:51,150
Bao as in "baby."

47
00:02:51,430 --> 00:02:52,540
Here you go, kid.

48
00:02:53,550 --> 00:02:55,560
Are you from the same village as my grandma?

49
00:02:57,150 --> 00:02:58,360
Then where do you live?

50
00:02:58,990 --> 00:03:00,270
I forgot.

51
00:03:04,790 --> 00:03:05,790
Adopted?

52
00:03:05,810 --> 00:03:07,030
What were you thinking?

53
00:03:07,350 --> 00:03:08,310
Calm down.

54
00:03:08,510 --> 00:03:09,760
Aren't I here to discuss it with you?

55
00:03:09,790 --> 00:03:10,710
What's there to discuss?

56
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,070
It's already been decided!

57
00:03:12,510 --> 00:03:13,420
I'm going to talk to Maotian.

58
00:03:13,420 --> 00:03:14,770
Why isn't he back yet?

59
00:03:15,870 --> 00:03:16,430
Mom.

60
00:03:16,550 --> 00:03:18,470
I'm in charge of this family now.

61
00:03:18,510 --> 00:03:20,510
If there's anything going on, you should tell me.

62
00:03:20,510 --> 00:03:21,670
What is there to tell you?

63
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:23,350
It's a major matter of the Xia family!

64
00:03:23,630 --> 00:03:25,170
Outsiders should keep their mouths shut!

65
00:03:25,230 --> 00:03:27,130
Mom, Mom, calm down.

66
00:03:27,230 --> 00:03:28,640
Let me talk to my sister-in-law.

67
00:03:29,350 --> 00:03:30,579
Sister-in-law.

68
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:33,220
I have to criticize you a bit.

69
00:03:33,270 --> 00:03:37,150
Our Xia family has three branches with over a dozen people,

70
00:03:37,230 --> 00:03:38,230
with my brother being the only male...

71
00:03:38,230 --> 00:03:39,990
Wasn't it originally five branches?

72
00:03:39,990 --> 00:03:41,410
Why are there only three branches now?

73
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:42,640
Where did the other two go?

74
00:03:42,730 --> 00:03:43,950
Whatever, it doesn't matter.

75
00:03:43,980 --> 00:03:45,420
Whether it's three branches or five,

76
00:03:45,510 --> 00:03:47,000
shouldn't we all live our own separate lives?

77
00:03:47,020 --> 00:03:48,700
When Maotian and I first came here,

78
00:03:48,730 --> 00:03:49,980
life was so hard,

79
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:52,620
yet I didn't see any of you guys caring about us.

80
00:03:53,110 --> 00:03:54,850
Who told you guys to leave back then?

81
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:56,790
If you didn't drag him away,

82
00:03:56,790 --> 00:03:59,740
would Maotian have left home to make a living?

83
00:03:59,790 --> 00:04:01,760
Why don't you take him back then?

84
00:04:01,790 --> 00:04:03,290
I'm not getting involved in this.

85
00:04:03,310 --> 00:04:04,170
Mom.

86
00:04:04,470 --> 00:04:05,130
Honghong.

87
00:04:06,950 --> 00:04:08,120
Son, you're back!

88
00:04:09,340 --> 00:04:11,110
I missed you so much.

89
00:04:12,430 --> 00:04:13,140
Gosh.

90
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,770
You've lost weight.

91
00:04:14,950 --> 00:04:15,590
Look how thin you've become.

92
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:17,300
Look at my brother, he's all sweaty.

93
00:04:17,329 --> 00:04:18,700
-He's sweating all over.
-Mom,

94
00:04:18,810 --> 00:04:22,010
there must be a reason why you and Honghong are back, right?

95
00:04:22,070 --> 00:04:23,310
You're finally back.

96
00:04:23,340 --> 00:04:24,590
Listen to what your mother has to say.

97
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:28,110
It's good news, wonderful news!

98
00:04:28,110 --> 00:04:28,950
Wonderful news!

99
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:31,240
You couldn't find better news even if you searched with a lantern!

100
00:04:31,430 --> 00:04:32,290
You couldn't!

101
00:04:32,390 --> 00:04:33,710
What good news?

102
00:04:34,150 --> 00:04:35,159
Your mother

103
00:04:35,230 --> 00:04:36,920
thinks Fenghua isn't good enough because she's a girl,

104
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:39,190
so she bought you a boy from someone else

105
00:04:39,350 --> 00:04:40,800
to be our son.

106
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:47,020
Isn't it great news?

107
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,290
It's great, isn't it?

108
00:04:48,540 --> 00:04:50,060
Now you have a son.

109
00:04:50,230 --> 00:04:52,180
The family line will continue.

110
00:04:52,230 --> 00:04:54,070
You're a father again!

111
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:55,750
I'm an aunt again!

112
00:04:55,790 --> 00:04:57,840
I have a grandson now!

113
00:04:58,060 --> 00:05:00,150
Look how happy my brother is.

114
00:05:00,230 --> 00:05:01,070
What?

115
00:05:01,470 --> 00:05:02,230
Is that true?

116
00:05:02,260 --> 00:05:03,410
Grandma told me that

117
00:05:03,510 --> 00:05:05,430
your family only has one daughter

118
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:08,220
and there is no male heir, so I'm here to be the son.

119
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:11,760
In the future, I'll get all the family inheritance.

120
00:05:12,550 --> 00:05:13,510
Family inheritance?

121
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,240
Did my grandma not tell you

122
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,150
about our family's situation?

123
00:05:16,350 --> 00:05:17,480
Your family has a big ship,

124
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:18,840
weighing around a thousand tons, right?

125
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:24,560
This kid is so mischievous.

126
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:26,840
Fenghua, who is he?

127
00:05:30,910 --> 00:05:31,580
Mom!

128
00:05:32,130 --> 00:05:33,710
What were you thinking!

129
00:05:33,790 --> 00:05:34,950
What era are we living in?

130
00:05:34,970 --> 00:05:36,090
How can your thinking still be so feudal?

131
00:05:36,190 --> 00:05:37,610
I'm not being feudal!

132
00:05:37,670 --> 00:05:38,710
It's because

133
00:05:38,820 --> 00:05:39,670
girls

134
00:05:39,790 --> 00:05:41,620
can't be recorded in the family genealogy!

135
00:05:41,670 --> 00:05:42,750
If you don't have a son,

136
00:05:42,770 --> 00:05:44,430
who will continue your family line when you get old?

137
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:45,720
Who will?

138
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,270
If it can't be continued, then so be it!

139
00:05:48,210 --> 00:05:48,800
I don't even know what I'm doing with my life yet!

140
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,800
Isn't that Fenghua's grandma?

141
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:51,909
Who can control what happens after death?

142
00:05:51,930 --> 00:05:53,010
Son!

143
00:05:53,230 --> 00:05:53,950
Then our Xia Family

144
00:05:53,950 --> 00:05:55,820
will have no descendants!

145
00:05:56,230 --> 00:05:58,290
Back in the Jiajing period, our Xia Family

146
00:05:58,310 --> 00:06:00,340
was a prestigious clan!

147
00:06:00,380 --> 00:06:02,700
The family genealogy is this thick!

148
00:06:02,750 --> 00:06:05,110
I can't allow our bloodline to stop here

149
00:06:05,110 --> 00:06:06,060
just because of you

150
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:07,630
and your good-for-nothing wife!

151
00:06:07,650 --> 00:06:09,730
Aren't you worried that your father wouldn't be able to rest in peace?

152
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:11,910
Our father wouldn't be able to rest in peace!

153
00:06:11,930 --> 00:06:13,490
My father wouldn't be that petty!

154
00:06:14,550 --> 00:06:18,020
God! God!

155
00:06:18,050 --> 00:06:19,450
Mom. Mom.

156
00:06:19,470 --> 00:06:20,850
Oh, my darling!

157
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:22,690
Come out and see this!

158
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:23,330
Mom.

159
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,610
Stop crying. Stop it.

160
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:27,040
Look at your good-for-nothing son!

161
00:06:27,070 --> 00:06:28,970
Mom.

162
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:29,760
Mom.

163
00:06:29,850 --> 00:06:30,990
Get up.

164
00:06:31,020 --> 00:06:32,710
You're just upset that we don't have a son, right?

165
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:35,140
It's simple. Just let your son divorce me

166
00:06:35,170 --> 00:06:36,980
and find someone else to give birth to a son for your family!

167
00:06:37,010 --> 00:06:37,659
What are you talking about?

168
00:06:37,690 --> 00:06:38,130
Let me tell you.

169
00:06:38,150 --> 00:06:40,050
I, Li Yan, am content with just having a daughter.

170
00:06:40,090 --> 00:06:41,370
I absolutely won't raise someone else's child!

171
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:43,000
Enough, can't you just endure a little?

172
00:06:43,030 --> 00:06:43,670
Haven't I endured enough?

173
00:06:43,690 --> 00:06:44,770
You don't get to decide!

174
00:06:44,810 --> 00:06:46,600
You don't get to decide.

175
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:47,909
I don't get to decide my family's affairs?

176
00:06:47,950 --> 00:06:49,230
What, so you're to decide them?

177
00:06:49,300 --> 00:06:51,110
Mom, look, the neighbors are all here.

178
00:06:51,110 --> 00:06:53,090
Let's talk back inside.

179
00:06:53,230 --> 00:06:54,750
I'm not going inside! I'm not going inside!

180
00:06:54,750 --> 00:06:55,950
Look at her! Just look at her!

181
00:06:55,990 --> 00:06:56,830
She's doing this on purpose!

182
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:57,930
It's all your fault!

183
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:01,870
Stop it, okay?

184
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:03,660
You wicked woman!

185
00:07:09,710 --> 00:07:10,510
What do you want?

186
00:07:10,630 --> 00:07:11,910
All of you, stop it!

187
00:07:11,910 --> 00:07:14,500
Who are you putting on a show for?

188
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:25,670
Sister.

189
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:27,750
Don't call me that.

190
00:07:27,780 --> 00:07:28,870
I'm not your sister.

191
00:07:29,190 --> 00:07:31,080
My father won't let you in our family.

192
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:32,390
Why?

193
00:07:32,430 --> 00:07:33,270
You're just a little kid.

194
00:07:33,310 --> 00:07:34,820
I don't need to explain myself to you.

195
00:07:34,850 --> 00:07:37,170
I don't eat much, and I'm easy to feed.

196
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:40,230
I also won't take the family inheritance away from you.

197
00:07:43,260 --> 00:07:44,500
Then why are you here?

198
00:07:44,870 --> 00:07:46,110
Before Grandma bought me,

199
00:07:46,130 --> 00:07:48,520
I hadn't eaten for three days.

200
00:07:48,550 --> 00:07:50,760
I want to live. I don't want to die.

201
00:07:58,920 --> 00:07:59,750
What do you want to eat?

202
00:07:59,770 --> 00:08:01,000
Let me think.

203
00:08:01,420 --> 00:08:01,850
Let's go.

204
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:02,790
Fenghua!

205
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:04,570
Fenghua!

206
00:08:05,110 --> 00:08:07,100
Do you know something happened to your family?

207
00:08:07,630 --> 00:08:08,900
Yeah, he just told me.

208
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:10,400
So it's you.

209
00:08:10,890 --> 00:08:12,880
Behave yourself, you hear me?

210
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:13,790
Pretty impressive.

211
00:08:15,530 --> 00:08:16,830
Your grandma must be crazy.

212
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:18,310
How can she do something like this?

213
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:21,150
You once said

214
00:08:21,350 --> 00:08:23,730
that you'd fight anyone who dared to bully me.

215
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:26,820
My grandma, I'll leave her to you.

216
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:34,020
You guys, give up already.

217
00:08:34,140 --> 00:08:35,539
I won't give birth to or raise any more children.

218
00:08:35,570 --> 00:08:38,110
I'm content with having one daughter in my life.

219
00:08:38,309 --> 00:08:39,809
If you want to complain about only having one male in three branches,

220
00:08:39,830 --> 00:08:41,010
you can raise him yourself.

221
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:44,039
Let him be Maotian's little brother.

222
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,430
Listen to her. Just listen.

223
00:08:45,430 --> 00:08:47,030
Is that how a human being talks?

224
00:08:47,060 --> 00:08:48,060
You're right.

225
00:08:48,460 --> 00:08:50,010
I'm not a human being.

226
00:08:50,060 --> 00:08:51,950
Ever since I married into Xia Family,

227
00:08:52,190 --> 00:08:53,270
I've been treated like a dog.

228
00:08:53,300 --> 00:08:54,730
I'm even worth less than a dog!

229
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:56,130
The year I gave birth to Fenghua,

230
00:08:56,230 --> 00:08:57,410
during my postpartum confinement,

231
00:08:57,650 --> 00:08:59,240
did any of you ever cook a meal for me

232
00:08:59,300 --> 00:09:00,770
or wash a single diaper?

233
00:09:00,930 --> 00:09:03,570
Fenghua would cry all night long,

234
00:09:03,590 --> 00:09:04,500
and I would spend night after night

235
00:09:04,530 --> 00:09:06,500
pacing back and forth in the room, holding her.

236
00:09:06,810 --> 00:09:08,810
How many days did I go without a full night's sleep?

237
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:10,570
But did any of you guys ever help me?

238
00:09:10,740 --> 00:09:12,940
Poor Fenghua had it even worse.

239
00:09:13,190 --> 00:09:14,510
Other children were loved by their grandma and grandpa,

240
00:09:14,530 --> 00:09:16,000
but not her.

241
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:18,530
As soon as she was born and you saw she was a girl,

242
00:09:18,560 --> 00:09:19,700
you didn't even look at her.

243
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:20,910
You just left.

244
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:23,950
Whenever you saw her, you always belittled her with snide remarks.

245
00:09:24,590 --> 00:09:26,640
How do you think that made she feel?

246
00:09:28,030 --> 00:09:29,400
When she was little, she used to ask me,

247
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,840
"Why does Grandma hate me so much?"

248
00:09:31,860 --> 00:09:33,220
"Am I really your child?"

249
00:09:33,250 --> 00:09:34,700
"Was I picked up by the river?"

250
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,960
I wouldn't have picked her up even if I found her.

251
00:09:36,140 --> 00:09:37,490
I wouldn't have taken her even if she were given to us for free.

252
00:09:39,550 --> 00:09:41,190
I dare you guys to say that again!

253
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:42,550
What if I say it again?

254
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:43,190
I wouldn't have taken her even if she were given to us for free.

255
00:09:43,190 --> 00:09:43,750
Don't you dare

256
00:09:43,750 --> 00:09:44,910
say things like that about my daughter again!

257
00:09:44,940 --> 00:09:46,390
If you are so capable, give birth to a son yourself!

258
00:09:46,410 --> 00:09:47,380
What nonsense are you talking about?

259
00:09:48,130 --> 00:09:48,870
You know what?

260
00:09:48,870 --> 00:09:49,630
He is my son!

261
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:50,550
I can't stand you people anymore!

262
00:09:50,550 --> 00:09:52,310
If you've got the guts, give me a boy!

263
00:09:52,310 --> 00:09:53,630
I'm very happy with the daughter I gave birth to!

264
00:09:53,630 --> 00:09:55,030
Why must I have a son?

265
00:09:55,310 --> 00:09:57,010
-Enough!
-I'm not ashamed at all!

266
00:09:58,870 --> 00:10:01,420
Will you guys ever stop?

267
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,430
I'm begging you guys.

268
00:10:03,430 --> 00:10:05,760
Save me some face, okay?

269
00:10:08,350 --> 00:10:10,810
We'll discuss the child matter later.

270
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:11,740
There's no room for discussion!

271
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:14,320
Let me tell you, Xia Maotian.

272
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:17,730
I, Li Yan, will only have one child in this lifetime,

273
00:10:18,470 --> 00:10:19,950
and that's our Fenghua!

274
00:10:20,430 --> 00:10:21,380
As for other people's children,

275
00:10:21,410 --> 00:10:22,630
whoever wants to raise them can do so.

276
00:10:23,060 --> 00:10:24,680
If you dare to give in,

277
00:10:25,570 --> 00:10:26,870
I'll divorce you!

278
00:10:33,790 --> 00:10:34,350
Brother.

279
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:36,620
You are the head of the household.

280
00:10:51,910 --> 00:10:53,160
Eat slowly.

281
00:10:55,470 --> 00:10:56,290
Here you go.

282
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:06,650
[Special price for a set: 18 yuan]

283
00:11:09,260 --> 00:11:10,070
What are you going to do?

284
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:12,750
Don't worry.

285
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:14,540
My mom will never agree.

286
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:15,880
If she really gets pushed to her limit,

287
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:17,150
she will divorce my dad.

288
00:11:17,730 --> 00:11:19,390
That's exactly what makes it troublesome.

289
00:11:19,830 --> 00:11:20,750
Your dad is filial.

290
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:22,170
He always listens to your grandmother.

291
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:23,880
If they really end up divorcing,

292
00:11:24,260 --> 00:11:25,680
you'll feel guilty, right?

293
00:11:32,230 --> 00:11:34,860
This kind of thing would never happen in your family.

294
00:11:36,070 --> 00:11:37,950
Things would be so much better if I were a boy.

295
00:11:46,270 --> 00:11:47,070
I think,

296
00:11:47,670 --> 00:11:50,120
your dad might not be able to handle this alone.

297
00:11:50,460 --> 00:11:51,380
We need to get help from the outside.

298
00:11:52,310 --> 00:11:53,070
What kind of help?

299
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:57,480
Maotian.

300
00:11:57,630 --> 00:11:58,260
Maotian!

301
00:11:59,340 --> 00:12:00,680
Don't be a coward this time.

302
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:01,670
Otherwise, your wife and daughter

303
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:03,920
will be bullied to death by your mother.

304
00:12:04,860 --> 00:12:05,700
Boss Xie.

305
00:12:06,150 --> 00:12:07,790
I'm not stupid.

306
00:12:08,470 --> 00:12:10,800
How could I possibly agree to such a ridiculous thing?

307
00:12:10,820 --> 00:12:12,470
What did you tell your mother just now?

308
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:14,160
You said you'd discuss it later!

309
00:12:14,700 --> 00:12:15,930
That's my mother.

310
00:12:16,180 --> 00:12:17,660
How can I disobey her?

311
00:12:17,860 --> 00:12:19,620
Well, disobedience,

312
00:12:19,690 --> 00:12:20,910
in the ancient times and

313
00:12:20,940 --> 00:12:22,700
in the Confucian culture,

314
00:12:22,730 --> 00:12:23,730
was considered unfilial.

315
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:24,670
If you were unfilial,

316
00:12:24,700 --> 00:12:25,690
people might laugh at you,

317
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,030
and you might even end up in jail.

318
00:12:27,050 --> 00:12:29,270
But what era are we living in now?

319
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:31,240
You need to have a broader vision

320
00:12:31,260 --> 00:12:32,430
when tackling issues.

321
00:12:32,460 --> 00:12:34,060
You can't just stick to the old ways.

322
00:12:34,390 --> 00:12:36,220
No matter how society develops,

323
00:12:36,370 --> 00:12:37,590
people still need to be filial, right?

324
00:12:37,610 --> 00:12:39,170
Sure. Of course you should be filial,

325
00:12:39,190 --> 00:12:40,440
but you can't be blindly filial.

326
00:12:40,460 --> 00:12:41,550
Exactly!

327
00:12:41,820 --> 00:12:42,750
Let me tell you,

328
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,320
at a time like this,

329
00:12:44,350 --> 00:12:46,840
if you don't think from your wife and daughter's perspective,

330
00:12:47,220 --> 00:12:48,400
and their hearts end up getting broken,

331
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,280
there will be no turning back.

332
00:12:49,710 --> 00:12:50,670
It's too late already!

333
00:12:51,660 --> 00:12:53,040
Xia Maotian, listen to me.

334
00:12:53,070 --> 00:12:54,980
Go back and be your mom's filial son.

335
00:12:55,010 --> 00:12:55,970
From now on,

336
00:12:56,300 --> 00:12:57,440
I'll take care of Fenghua,

337
00:12:57,470 --> 00:12:58,350
and we'll live on our own.

338
00:12:58,530 --> 00:13:00,660
You go your way, and I'll go mine.

339
00:13:00,700 --> 00:13:02,150
From this point on, we part ways!

340
00:13:02,950 --> 00:13:03,700
Mom!

341
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:05,070
What are you doing?

342
00:13:05,070 --> 00:13:05,910
You guys...

343
00:13:05,950 --> 00:13:06,430
Alright, stop it.

344
00:13:06,430 --> 00:13:07,550
We can live just fine without a man!

345
00:13:07,550 --> 00:13:08,390
Let's go! Let's go!

346
00:13:08,430 --> 00:13:08,830
Mom!

347
00:13:08,850 --> 00:13:10,340
Dad! Talk some sense into Mom!

348
00:13:10,390 --> 00:13:11,780
She's not just saying this out of anger!

349
00:13:11,780 --> 00:13:12,470
You see?

350
00:13:12,530 --> 00:13:13,560
She's always talking about getting a divorce!

351
00:13:13,590 --> 00:13:14,630
Always threatening to divorce me!

352
00:13:14,660 --> 00:13:15,930
I can't live like this anymore!

353
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:17,680
Hey, you guys...

354
00:13:18,710 --> 00:13:19,660
Stand up!

355
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:24,100
Act like a man!

356
00:13:35,210 --> 00:13:36,470
Mom, I...

357
00:13:36,490 --> 00:13:38,770
What kind of photo is this?

358
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:39,760
So ugly.

359
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:46,740
Mom.

360
00:13:47,310 --> 00:13:48,390
I've made up my mind.

361
00:13:49,110 --> 00:13:51,360
Yan and I can't raise this child.

362
00:13:51,380 --> 00:13:52,510
You must raise him!

363
00:13:52,850 --> 00:13:54,100
Our Xia family

364
00:13:54,130 --> 00:13:56,360
