365
00:13:56,550 --> 00:13:58,430
If you don't raise him, I'm not leaving!

366
00:13:58,540 --> 00:14:00,020
I'm going to live here!

367
00:14:01,470 --> 00:14:03,040
Living here seems quite nice.

368
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,190
The bed is so soft and comfortable.

369
00:14:04,210 --> 00:14:06,050
Brother, why didn't you buy one for Mom?

370
00:14:06,190 --> 00:14:07,770
He doesn't care about me at all!

371
00:14:08,250 --> 00:14:08,950
Brother,

372
00:14:09,780 --> 00:14:11,670
