379
00:14:22,830 --> 00:14:23,910
Isn't that great?

380
00:14:23,950 --> 00:14:25,350
What era are we living in?

381
00:14:25,390 --> 00:14:27,030
Who still cares about family genealogy?

382
00:14:27,030 --> 00:14:28,070
I do!

383
00:14:28,190 --> 00:14:29,350
Your children

384
00:14:29,380 --> 00:14:31,150
and every following generation will!

385
00:14:31,860 --> 00:14:34,020
When we're alive, we are members of the Xia family,

386
00:14:34,070 --> 00:14:34,950
and even after we die,

387
00:14:34,980 --> 00:14:37,600
