388
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:41,520
We... We cannot forget our ancestors!

389
00:14:41,550 --> 00:14:42,790
We can't.

390
00:14:48,630 --> 00:14:49,950
There are no outsiders here.

391
00:14:50,540 --> 00:14:53,490
You don't have to keep up the act anymore.

392
00:14:55,210 --> 00:14:56,550
What are you talking about?

393
00:14:56,580 --> 00:14:57,940
What act am I putting on?

394
00:14:57,980 --> 00:14:59,300
Stop acting, okay?

395
00:14:59,660 --> 00:15:00,900
Last week,

396
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:02,860
the village secretary called me.

397
00:15:02,900 --> 00:15:04,850
What's a village secretary?

398
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:07,620
He explained everything very clearly.

399
00:15:09,030 --> 00:15:10,270
What did he tell you?

400
00:15:10,310 --> 00:15:12,550
He said someone's interested in our village's land

401
00:15:13,610 --> 00:15:15,560
