402
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,830
What's a photovoltaic base?

403
00:15:16,850 --> 00:15:17,570
Stop talking.

404
00:15:19,260 --> 00:15:20,180
The relocation compensation

405
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:22,230
