411
00:15:31,070 --> 00:15:31,710
Don't listen to him!

412
00:15:31,710 --> 00:15:33,000
Don't you worry.

413
00:15:33,190 --> 00:15:35,340
I won't take a penny of that relocation money.

414
00:15:35,370 --> 00:15:36,900
You and Honghong can take it all.

415
00:15:36,930 --> 00:15:37,520
Brother!

416
00:15:37,550 --> 00:15:38,860
Keep your voice down!

417
00:15:39,760 --> 00:15:40,810
Brother...

418
00:15:40,830 --> 00:15:41,910
Brother, sit down.

419
00:15:41,930 --> 00:15:43,110
Don't be anxious.

420
00:15:43,130 --> 00:15:44,020
Listen.

421
00:15:44,040 --> 00:15:45,660
I won't agree with this.

422
00:15:45,690 --> 00:15:46,790
No matter what,

423
00:15:46,810 --> 00:15:48,220
you're still a part of the Xia family,

424
00:15:48,260 --> 00:15:50,580
and you're the only male. As long as...

425
00:15:50,610 --> 00:15:52,640
Let me finish first.

426
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:55,360
We won't take the money,

427
00:15:55,990 --> 00:15:58,040
but you have to take the child with you.

428
00:15:58,180 --> 00:15:59,840
If you don't trust me,

429
00:16:00,370 --> 00:16:02,190
we can go to the notary office

430
00:16:02,210 --> 00:16:04,490
and sign a transferring contract for the relocation compensation.

431
00:16:05,900 --> 00:16:07,170
But I'm begging you guys,

432
00:16:07,760 --> 00:16:08,550
from now on,

433
00:16:08,570 --> 00:16:10,570
don't come and upset my wife and daughter anymore.

434
00:16:10,610 --> 00:16:11,570
Can you do that?

435
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:14,700
Those two... They're my life.

436
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:18,300
Brother. We won't do that. We won't.

437
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:20,230
Mom is just looking out for you,

438
00:16:20,310 --> 00:16:21,070
you know?

439
00:16:21,330 --> 00:16:22,550
Don't interrupt.

440
00:16:24,190 --> 00:16:26,640
Does Yan agree to this?

441
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:30,080
If you take this child away,

442
00:16:30,740 --> 00:16:33,790
we can earn the money ourselves.

443
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:36,150
So, this is settled then.

444
00:16:36,180 --> 00:16:38,110
Don't come saying that I forced you into this.

445
00:16:38,130 --> 00:16:39,110
Do you hear me?

446
00:16:39,510 --> 00:16:40,540
I'm doing this willingly.

447
00:16:40,770 --> 00:16:41,900
I won't go back on my word!

448
00:16:42,510 --> 00:16:43,230
Fenghua.

449
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:44,860
It's okay.

450
00:16:44,890 --> 00:16:45,980
You know,

451
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:48,310
your father actually loves you very much.

452
00:16:48,340 --> 00:16:49,220
Don't worry.

453
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:51,240
He won't let anyone hurt you.

454
00:16:52,860 --> 00:16:54,130
Why are you crying?

455
00:16:54,170 --> 00:16:56,110
You're usually so talkative,

456
00:16:56,150 --> 00:16:57,850
but you fall apart at crucial moments.

457
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:58,610
Alright, alright.

458
00:16:58,630 --> 00:16:59,590
I'm scared...

459
00:16:59,620 --> 00:17:00,500
Why are you scared?

460
00:17:00,520 --> 00:17:01,860
Your parents are still alive!

461
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:03,230
Whoever dares to bully my daughter,

462
00:17:03,260 --> 00:17:04,460
I'll fight them to death!

463
00:17:06,040 --> 00:17:07,380
Fenghua.

464
00:17:08,230 --> 00:17:09,380
Fenghua.

465
00:17:10,470 --> 00:17:11,700
Let me say a few words.

466
00:17:12,589 --> 00:17:14,240
A good dog doesn't block the way.

467
00:17:14,270 --> 00:17:15,609
Sorry, I'll make way for you.

468
00:17:15,890 --> 00:17:17,040
I'm not talking about you.

469
00:17:17,589 --> 00:17:18,560
Fenghua.

470
00:17:18,579 --> 00:17:21,000
Grandma was thoughtless this time.

471
00:17:21,069 --> 00:17:22,540
I'm sorry for the trouble I've caused you two.

472
00:17:22,569 --> 00:17:23,730
I was wrong.

473
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:24,390
From now on,

474
00:17:24,430 --> 00:17:25,329
just

475
00:17:25,359 --> 00:17:27,220
listen to your parents

476
00:17:27,250 --> 00:17:28,200
and be filial to them.

477
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:29,640
Grandma's leaving now.

478
00:17:29,670 --> 00:17:30,390
You talk.

479
00:17:31,420 --> 00:17:32,430
What about the child?

480
00:17:32,520 --> 00:17:34,520
Didn't you say you wouldn't raise this child?

481
00:17:34,560 --> 00:17:36,290
I'll take him back, and someone will raise him.

482
00:17:36,330 --> 00:17:38,860
Our family isn't the only one in the village short of male heirs.

483
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:41,880
If you don't want him, others will.

484
00:17:43,510 --> 00:17:44,030
Sister!

485
00:17:44,540 --> 00:17:45,890
Let's go, let's go.

486
00:17:47,120 --> 00:17:47,740
We're leaving.

487
00:17:47,790 --> 00:17:48,390
Take care.

488
00:17:48,420 --> 00:17:48,760
Come on.

489
00:17:48,790 --> 00:17:49,430
Maotian.

490
00:17:50,050 --> 00:17:52,390
This... I just bought this!

491
00:17:52,430 --> 00:17:53,990
Buy another one.

492
00:17:56,510 --> 00:17:58,490
The rice is still in the cooker!

493
00:17:58,740 --> 00:17:59,870
Mom! Mom!

494
00:18:02,980 --> 00:18:03,980
Alright, I'm leaving now.

495
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,490
I was cooking, too.

496
00:18:05,520 --> 00:18:06,490
Alright. Alright.

497
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:11,990
So they gave in?

498
00:18:12,020 --> 00:18:12,630
Yeah, they did.

499
00:18:15,320 --> 00:18:16,080
Hey.

500
00:18:16,390 --> 00:18:17,260
We'll buy another one.

501
00:18:17,630 --> 00:18:18,910
Don't give everything...

502
00:18:18,950 --> 00:18:19,790
Alright, alright.

503
00:18:19,830 --> 00:18:21,110
Go back, no need to see us off.

504
00:18:21,190 --> 00:18:22,070
Give this to me.

505
00:18:22,100 --> 00:18:22,780
Hurry up and go.

506
00:18:22,790 --> 00:18:24,130
No need to see us off.

507
00:18:24,890 --> 00:18:26,190
Uncle, it's that kid!

508
00:18:26,220 --> 00:18:26,930
Okay.

509
00:18:31,270 --> 00:18:32,150
Don't block the way.

510
00:18:32,170 --> 00:18:33,690
If we're late, we'll miss the bus.

511
00:18:33,720 --> 00:18:35,260
Don't rush, old lady.

512
00:18:35,420 --> 00:18:36,660
Excuse me, may I ask

513
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:37,880
