514
00:18:37,980 --> 00:18:38,790
He is...

515
00:18:38,870 --> 00:18:40,390
He's my relative's child.

516
00:18:40,410 --> 00:18:41,620
Do you have his ID card?

517
00:18:41,650 --> 00:18:42,860
He's too young,

518
00:18:42,890 --> 00:18:43,630
so we haven't had the chance to get him one yet.

519
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:44,570
She bought me...

520
00:18:44,600 --> 00:18:45,550
Don't talk nonsense!

521
00:18:45,570 --> 00:18:46,590
If you keep talking nonsense, I'll beat you!

522
00:18:46,630 --> 00:18:48,030
I'll actually beat you!

523
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:49,000
Come here.

524
00:18:49,910 --> 00:18:50,560
Come on.

525
00:18:51,220 --> 00:18:52,030
Little boy.

526
00:18:52,620 --> 00:18:54,590
-I'm a police officer.
-What's going on now?

527
00:18:54,620 --> 00:18:56,610
Don't be afraid. Say whatever you want.

528
00:18:56,660 --> 00:18:57,630
Officer.

529
00:18:57,670 --> 00:18:58,990
I lied to you just now.

530
00:18:59,020 --> 00:19:01,560
We actually picked up this child on the street.

531
00:19:01,590 --> 00:19:02,640
I've heard of picking up money,

532
00:19:02,670 --> 00:19:03,520
but picking up a child?

533
00:19:04,190 --> 00:19:05,810
You think police officers are that easy to fool?

534
00:19:05,830 --> 00:19:07,380
Officer, please save me!

535
00:19:07,420 --> 00:19:09,230
Bad people kidnapped me.

536
00:19:09,260 --> 00:19:10,530
My dad's name is Zhang Liangyong.

537
00:19:10,560 --> 00:19:11,940
My mom's name is Liu Cuiying.

538
00:19:11,970 --> 00:19:14,510
I don't know where my home is. I've forgotten everything.

539
00:19:14,540 --> 00:19:15,110
Come on.

540
00:19:16,470 --> 00:19:17,670
Come with me.

541
00:19:17,780 --> 00:19:18,390
Come here.

542
00:19:20,430 --> 00:19:21,910
Child trafficking, huh?

543
00:19:22,290 --> 00:19:24,570
No, Officer!

544
00:19:24,600 --> 00:19:25,480
Get up first.

545
00:19:25,510 --> 00:19:26,070
Come on, get up.

546
00:19:26,090 --> 00:19:26,590
Stand up and talk.

547
00:19:27,250 --> 00:19:28,820
Our family needs a male heir,

548
00:19:28,840 --> 00:19:30,640
and the neighbors had two boys,

549
00:19:30,670 --> 00:19:32,140
so they gave us one.

550
00:19:32,160 --> 00:19:33,660
I even had to pay them!

551
00:19:33,720 --> 00:19:35,630
I don't know anything else!

552
00:19:35,710 --> 00:19:37,390
Brother, help our mom!

553
00:19:37,390 --> 00:19:37,710
Shen.

554
00:19:37,710 --> 00:19:38,410
Shen.

555
00:19:38,490 --> 00:19:39,880
This must be a misunderstanding.

556
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:41,140
This must be a misunderstanding!

557
00:19:41,170 --> 00:19:43,640
My mom is uneducated and doesn't understand the law.

558
00:19:43,870 --> 00:19:45,580
She's old and muddled.

559
00:19:45,620 --> 00:19:47,320
We'll leave the child to you.

560
